**Summary:** API reference documentation for the SuperTokens OpenTelemetry Node.js plugin (`@supertokens-plugins/opentelemetry-nodejs`) that provides distributed tracing capabilities through the PluginImpl class with methods for span management, tracer initialization, attribute transformation, and tracing header generation for core API calls.

